3. Add Smart `.gitignore` (prevents pushing secrets / blobs)

```bash
cat > .gitignore <<'EOF'
# Secrets
.env
*.key
*.pem

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.pytest_cache/
*.egg-info/

# Data & models (regenerable)
